  "common": {
    "name": {
      "zh": "CheyTac M200 \"干预\" .408 CT 栓动式狙击步枪（FDE）。",
      "en": "CheyTac M200 Intervention .408 CT bolt-action sniper rifle (FDE)"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "M200",
      "en": "M200"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "CheyTac Intervention，又称CheyTac M200，是由美国CheyTac公司生产的栓动狙击步枪，亦可归类为反器材步枪。该枪采用七发可拆卸单排弹匣供弹（亦可选配五发弹匣）。CheyTac公司宣称该系统能在2500码（2286米）射程内保持低于1MOA的精度。",
      "en": "The CheyTac Intervention, also known as the CheyTac M200, is an American bolt-action sniper rifle manufactured by CheyTac USA, which can also be classified as an anti-materiel rifle. It is fed by a seven-round detachable single-stack magazine (an optional five-round magazine is also available). CheyTac Inc. states that the system is capable of delivering sub-MOA accuracy at ranges of up to 2,500 yd (2,286 m)."
    },
